"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\">",
"    <table cellspacing=\"0\">",
"     <tbody>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td class=\"subtitle1\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\">",
"        Therapy",
"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"subtitle1\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\">",
"        Documented",
"effect",
"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"subtitle1\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\">",
"        Strength of evidence",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td class=\"subtitle2\">",
"        Symptoms",
"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"subtitle2\">",
"        Ischemia",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        TENS",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        +",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        +",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        B",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        SCS",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        +",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        +",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        A",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        TMR",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        +",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        ?",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        A",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        PLR",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        +",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        ?",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        B",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        LSGB",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        +",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        ?",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        C",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"     </tbody>",
"    </table>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     TENS: transcutaneous electrical nerve stimulation; SCS: spinal cord stimulation; TMR: transmyocardial laser revascularization; PLR: percutaneous laser revascularization; LSGB: left stellate ganglion blockade.",
"     <br>",
"      Strength of evidence is based upon amount of scientific documentation: A: Well-designed, well-conducted, controlled trials (randomized and non-randomized) with statistically significant results that consistently support the recommendations. B: Observational studies or controlled trials with less consistent results to support the guideline recommendations. C: Expert opinion that supports the guideline recommendation because the available scientific evidence did not present consistent results, or controlled trials were lacking.",
"     </br>",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Data from Mannheimer C, Camicci P, Chester MR, et al. Eur Heart J 2002; 23:355.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
